<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %> - Volunteer Sign-up</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined') { %>
    <div data-error id="<%= error %>"></div>
  <% } %>

  <header>
    <nav>
      <div class="container">
        <a href="/" class="logo">Volunteer Sign-up</a>
        <ul class="nav-links">
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a></li>
          <li><a href="/profile">
            <img id="header_pfp"
              alt="Profile"
              src="/img/default_pfp.svg"
              width="30">
          </a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>Did you know?</h1>
    </section>
    <div class="statistics">
      <ul>
        <h2>U.S. Census: September 2023 Volunteer Statistics</h2>
        <h3>(Percentages are approximate)</h3>
        <li><%= (volunteerFreq * 100).toFixed(1) %>% answered 'Yes' to being a volunteer!</li>
        <li><%= (childrenActFreq * 100).toFixed(1) %>% of volunteers answered 'Yes' to helping with children's activities!</li>
        <li><%= (onlineFreq * 100).toFixed(1) %>% of volunteer work is done online!</li>
        <li>Volunteers spend, on average, <%= avgHours.toFixed(1) %> hours volunteering!</li>
        <li>Meanwhile, the median number of hours volunteered is <%= medHours %> hours!</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Volunteer Sign-up. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
